OL,3,CComplainants in Donaldson case 'not
OL,4,Creliable enough' for guilty verdict-
OL,5,C defence
OL,7,FContent warning: Readers may find some
OL,8,Fdetails in this article upsetting
OL,10,FTwo complainants who have accused Sir
OL,11,FJeffrey Donaldson of sexual offences
OL,12,Fare not "sufficiently reliable enough"
OL,13,Ffor the jury to find him guilty, a
OL,14,Fbarrister has told the court.
OL,16,FThe former DUP leader's barrister
OL,17,FKieran Vaughan also told the jury to
OL,18,F"ignore the noise and focus on the
OL,19,Fevidence" when they consider their
OL,20,Fverdicts.
OL,26,@tD@IOUtD@fO]zD@AOU{D@IO]
