OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781700487
OL,3,CComplainants in Donaldson case 'not
OL,4,Creliable enough' for guilty verdict-
OL,5,C defence
OL,7,FDonaldson, 63, has pleaded not guilty
OL,8,Fto 18 alleged offences.
OL,10,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,11,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,12,Fand gross indecency, and span a period
OL,13,Fbetween 1985 and 2008 involving two
OL,14,Falleged victims.
OL,16,FComplainants A and B have both given
OL,17,Fevidence at the trial.
OL,19,FBoth women allege they were abused as
OL,20,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
