PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781700487
OL,3,CComplainants in Donaldson case 'not
OL,4,Creliable enough' for guilty verdict-
OL,5,C defence
OL,7,FHe said her evidence about the alleged
OL,8,Fincident showed she "is a witness who
OL,9,Fis capable of telling a terrible
OL,10,Funtruth".
OL,12,FThe barrister said A was a witness who
OL,13,Fwas capable of "leaving things out of
OL,14,Fher evidence if she thinks it suits
OL,15,Fher own ends".
OL,17,FHe added that she was also capable of
OL,18,F"adding things in if she thinks it
OL,19,Fsuits her own ends".
OL,26,@pD@UOUrD@HO]uD@POUwD@MO]zD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781700487
OL,3,CComplainants in Donaldson case 'not
OL,4,Creliable enough' for guilty verdict-
OL,5,C defence
OL,7,FMr Vaughan said: "I end where I began
OL,8,F` ignore the noise, focus on the
OL,9,Fevidence."
OL,11,FHe said if the jury focused on the
OL,12,Fevidence "you will see there are
OL,13,Fsignificant and fundamental issues"
OL,14,Fwith the credibility of each of the
OL,15,Fcomplainants.
OL,17,FHe added: "They are not sufficiently
OL,18,Freliable enough to drive you to a sure
OL,19,Fconclusion that he is guilty."
OL,26,@oD@ROUqD@JO]tD@JOUuD@cO]yD@KOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
