OL,3,CComplainants in Donaldson case 'not
OL,4,Creliable enough' for guilty verdict-
OL,5,C defence
OL,7,FMr Vaughan invited the jury to find
OL,8,FDonaldson not guilty of all the
OL,9,Fallegations that he faces.
OL,11,FThe trial continues.
